name: CI Canadian REIT ETF
longDescription: The First Asset ETF's investment objective is to seek long-term total returns consisting of regular income and long term capital appreciation from an actively managed portfolio comprised primarily of securities of Canadian real estate investment trusts, real estate operating corporations and entities involved in real estate related services. The ETFs investment objective is to seek long term total returns consisting of regular income and long term capital appreciation from an actively managed portfolio comprised primarily of securities of Canadian REITs, REOCs and entities involved in real estate related services.
